messages.message:
@hannah @Jessica I have two PRs open covering all the changes to the API docs discussed here, including just straight up removing the webhooks section. I noted that it’s still supported via UI. I’ve added the `keys` parameter, revised the description of the `runtime_config` parameter, and also noticed that `post_processed_pdf_path` wasn’t included in our response schema so I added that in.

This is the PR for changes to the OpenAPI spec: https://github.com/instabase/aihub-openapi/pull/29/files
This is the PR for changes to the supporting Markdown files: https://github.com/instabase/instabase-fern/pull/221
